%r

library(ggplot2)

# Use Sepal length and width to predicts the flower species
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Sepal.Length, y = Sepal.Width, color=Species, shape=Species)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(method=lm, se=FALSE, fullrange=TRUE) + # Use logistic regression
  stat_ellipse() # Cluster the prediction
